<h2 id="netcolognegoesnative-0504" class="entry-title">NetCologne goes native!</h2>
<abbr class="updated" title="2013-04-05T13:42:00-00:00">Saturday, May 4th, 2013</abbr></header>
<div class="vcard" style="visibility: hidden">
	<a class="url fn" href="http://www.sixxs.net/">SixXS</a>
</div>
<div class="entry-content">
<div class="newslinksbox">
<a href="http://www.netcologne.de/ipv6" class="nolines"><img src="/s/pops/logos/netcologne.gif" alt="" /></a>
<div class="newslinks">
<a href="http://www.netcologne.de/ipv6" title="Link to related material">related link</a><br />
<a href="/news/2013/#netcolognegoesnative-0504" title="Permanent link to this article, useful for bookmarking" rel="bookmark">permlink</a>
</div>
</div>
<p>
<a href="http://www.netcologne.de/ipv6">NetCologne</a>, the host of the <a href="/pops/netcologne/">decgn01 PoP</a>, has announced that they are ready to provide native IPv6 over DSL to their customer base.
</p>
<p>
If you are a current or future NetCologne customer, check their <a href="http://www.netcologne.de/ipv6">IPv6 FAQ</a> for the exact details.
</p>

